Package: matools
Type: Package
Title: Mini Analysis Toolkit for R
Version: 1.0.0
Author: c(person("Taylor", "Fore", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "taylor.r.fore@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8144-613X")))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <taylor.r.fore@gmail.com>
Description: A toolkit for analyzing electrophysiology data - transform (.asc) files exported
    from Mini Analysis (Synaptosoft) into R data objects; calculate and plot common metrics
    used in neuroscience.
